{"tid":1892371,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"18:05 屯門公園現神蹟 輪椅長者竟能行走","createTime":"2020-02-22T13:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T15:02:41.000Z","uid":28114,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e48ed1f78c2d68ca006a87f751674456a7479ae0","tid":1892371,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:02:45.000Z","msg":"［科大振翅即時］18:05 #屯門<br />\n屯門公園現神蹟 輪椅長者竟能行走<br />\n<br />\n傍晚六時，警員撤出屯門公園，但長者仍與市民有零星口角。其中一名坐電動輪椅的長者播放紅歌抗衡市民的謾罵聲浪，爭執期間更被指出手推撞記者。<br />\n<br />\n口角期間，該名坐電動輪椅長者突然站起，向記者表示「我從來冇話過自己係瘸嘅」，更步伐流暢，走近與市民對罵，隨後登上電動輪椅，揚長而去。<br />\n<br />\n記者發現其電動輪椅上裝有倒後鏡及喇叭，相信輪椅是長者的座駕，而非必需品。<br />\n<br />\n註：相片未經處理，只是記者忍笑失敗，手震所致<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Wf5iau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Wf5iau.jpg&h=8f354541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkusteb/photos/a.195769800540041/2686892521427744/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkusteb%2Fphotos%2Fa.195769800540041%2F2686892521427744%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=28712c76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkusteb/photos/a.195769800540041/2686892521427744/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"2ba52cbeb445008e46f27715de42fb5124691ae9","tid":1892371,"uid":143382,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"屌你第三張圖個effect<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nJoJo咁款"},{"pid":"e6f90a5513c440f741ae5fb04e57a95990c1806d","tid":1892371,"uid":29649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:04:21.000Z","msg":"Deja vu"},{"pid":"14d19545205c4b35ac3516d3211fab23bf344a7d","tid":1892371,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"手震<img src=\